double threat - ...Nxe5 and ...Nc5. White's only move is} 16. Bd4 {when after
the unexpected} Nb8 $1 {[%csl Rd3,Rd4] the bishops are still hanging. The only
escape route is} 17. c5 Nc6 18. Bb5 $1 Nxd4 19. c6 Bc8 20. Rfd1 Nf3+ 21. gxf3
Qf6 $15 {Still, Black is slightly better in view of his superior structure and
safer king.} *

